Simple Badge for a GitHub organization using the GitHub JSONP API via jQuery, and the Lemmon Slider plugin.

I'm using Nearsoft 'cause Nearsoft rocks and that stuff. Change to fit your needs accordingly.

Settings:

target Where to put the badge. By default, the element from where you call the plugin
users Should I display the users? Default: true, // Requires Lemmon Slider!!!
repos Display number of public repos? Default: true,
gists Display number of public gists? Default: true,
organization Organization name (eg http://github.com/[useThisThing]) Default: 'nearsoft',
imgWidth Organization image width. Default: '50px'